OL,3,CWhy has a live-streamed murder trial
OL,4,Cin Kazakhstan sparked national outcry?
OL,6,FMs Nukenova, 31, was found dead in
OL,7,FNovember in a restaurant owned by one
OL,8,Fof her husband's relatives.
OL,10,FBishimbayev, who was charged with
OL,11,Ftorturing and killing his wife,
OL,12,Fmaintained his innocence for weeks but
OL,13,Fadmitted on Wednesday in court that he
OL,14,Fhad beaten her and.
OL,16,FHis lawyers initially disputed medical
OL,17,Fevidence indicating Ms Nukenova died
OL,18,Ffrom repeated blows to the head.
