OL,3,CWhy has a live-streamed murder trial
OL,4,Cin Kazakhstan sparked national outcry?
OL,6,FHuge swaths of the country's 19
OL,7,Fmillion residents have been watching
OL,8,Fthe trial unfold live.
OL,10,FCCTV footage serving as a key piece of
OL,11,Fevidence in the trial was also shown,
OL,12,Fand it was particularly disturbing.
OL,14,FBishimbayev is seen dragging his wife
OL,15,Fby her hair, and then punching and
OL,16,Fkicking her. Hours after it was
OL,17,Frecorded, she died of brain trauma.
