OL,3,CWhy has a live-streamed murder trial
OL,4,Cin Kazakhstan sparked national outcry?
OL,6,FThe 44-year-old Bishimbayev was once
OL,7,Fseen as a Western-educated face of
OL,8,FKazakhstan's government under former
OL,9,Fleader Nursultan Nazarbayev. But he
OL,10,Fwas then jailed for bribery in 2018
OL,11,Fbefore being pardoned fewer than two
OL,12,Fyears into his 10-year sentence.
OL,14,FThe trial is still underway and police
OL,15,Fare investigating telephone threats
OL,16,Freported by Judge Ayzhan Kulbayeva
OL,17,Fafter she disallowed forensic evidence
OL,18,Ffrom defence lawyers alleging Ms
OL,19,FNukenova's death could have been
OL,20,Fcaused by a preexisting condition.
