OL,3,CWhy has a live-streamed murder trial
OL,4,Cin Kazakhstan sparked national outcry?
OL,6,FThe next step in the trial will be the
OL,7,Fclosing arguments.
OL,9,FHow have people responded to the trial?
OL,11,FDays after Ms Nukenova's death, her
OL,12,Frelatives launched an online petition
OL,13,Furging authorities to pass "Saltanat's
OL,14,FLaw" to bolster protection for those
OL,15,Fat risk of domestic violence. It
OL,16,Fquickly got over 150,000 signatures.
OL,18,FAs Bishimbayev's trial began, more
OL,19,Fthan 5,000 Kazakhs wrote to senators ,
OL,20,Faccording to local media reports.
