OL,3,CWhy has a live-streamed murder trial
OL,4,Cin Kazakhstan sparked national outcry?
OL,6,FOn April 11, senators approved a bill
OL,7,Ftoughening spousal abuse laws, and
OL,8,FPresident Kassym-Jomart Tokayev signed
OL,9,Fit four days later.
OL,11,FAitbek Amangeldy, Ms Nukenova's elder
OL,12,Fbrother and a key prosecution witness,
OL,13,Fsaid he had no doubt his sister's
OL,14,Ftragic fate has shifted attitudes
OL,15,Fabout domestic violence.
OL,17,F"It changes people's minds when they
OL,18,Fsee directly what it looks like when a
OL,19,Fperson is tortured," Mr Amangeldy said
OL,20,Fin a video interview, citing the video
OL,21,Fplayed in court.
