OL,6,FMr Amangeldy added that the law's
OL,7,Ffinal version failed to include all
OL,8,Fthe provisions his family and allies
OL,9,Fhad wanted, noting that "we still have
OL,10,Fno legal norms around stalking and
OL,11,Fharassment" of adults.
OL,13,FThe proposals encountered fierce
OL,14,Fpushback from the Kazakh Union of
OL,15,FParents, an influential association
OL,16,Fthat echoes Russia's opposition to
OL,17,Ffeminist initiatives and LGBTQ+ rights.
