OL,6,FHow big a problem is domestic abuse in
OL,7,FKazakhstan?
OL,9,FAccording to a 2018 study backed by UN
OL,10,FWomen, the United Nations' gender
OL,11,Fequality agency, about 400 women die
OL,12,Ffrom domestic violence each year in
OL,13,FKazakhstan, although many abuse cases
OL,14,Fgo unreported.
