OL,3,CWhy has a live-streamed murder trial
OL,4,Cin Kazakhstan sparked national outcry?
OL,6,FIn 2017, Kazakhstan decriminalised
OL,7,Fbeatings and other acts causing
OL,8,F"minor" physical damage, making them
OL,9,Fpunishable only by fines or short jail
OL,10,Fterms. Russia enacted a similar law
OL,11,Fthat year, outraging women's rights
OL,12,Fadvocates.
OL,14,FKazakhstan's new law reverses this,
OL,15,Fincreasing penalties for assailants
OL,16,Fand introducing new criminal offences,
OL,17,Fincluding harassment of minors.
