OL,3,CWhy has a live-streamed murder trial
OL,4,Cin Kazakhstan sparked national outcry?
OL,6,FViktoriya Kim, a Kazakhstan-based
OL,7,Fresearcher at Human Rights Watch, said
OL,8,Fthe very notion of "domestic violence"
OL,9,Fis absent from the country's criminal
OL,10,Fcode. Including it, she said, would
OL,11,Fsend "a clearer signal."
OL,13,FBut Mr Amangeldy argued that Kazakh
OL,14,Fsociety has clearly "passed a point of
OL,15,Fno return."
OL,17,F"For years, across Kazakhstan and the
OL,18,Fwhole region, the issue (of domestic
OL,19,Fviolence) was shrouded in silence.
OL,20,FRaising the issue is already half the
OL,21,Fsolution," he said.
